archimate:ArchimateDiagramModel.name: Interoperability testing Plateau for ArchiMate with Archi, Magic Draw and Protégé

children.content:
1 -No access for the Business Actors organisation A/C/D to a modeling tool producing open format ArchiMate models
2 - The organisation A/C/D have another solutions which are based on heterogeneous modeling technologies
3- The ArchiMate models artifacts have to be integrated in heterogeneous platforms for different purpose: data linking based on semantic technologies, knowledge base relying on grakn.ai, or design platforms based on UML2/SysML.
4- All these solutions don't have a dedicated ArchiMate plugin but the idea is hovever being able to exchange and share the models relying on heterogeneous languages: polyglot hypermodel, i.e. consistent multiple representations of the same model using different langages, for different purpose
